tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE films (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  title TEXT,
  genre TEXT,
  release_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE films (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(255),
    genre VARCHAR(50),
    release_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE film_updates (
    update_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    film_id UUID,
    new_genre VARCHAR(50),
    updated_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE batch_updates (
    batch_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    description VARCHAR(255),
    executed BOOLEAN,
    executed_at TIMESTAMP
)
